## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential bias in sources, particularly those from advocacy groups or opinion-based platforms. Additionally, the legal context may vary significantly across different jurisdictions, which could affect the generalizability of the findings. Further research could explore the economic impact of strikes in more detail and consider international perspectives on labor rights.